Jesse Bradford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesse_Bradford 0 Jesse Bradford (born May 28, 1979) is an American actor. He began his career as a child actor at the age of five and received two Young Artist Award for Best Leading Young Actor in a Feature Film nominations.
